    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "`Accept error: accept tcp 127.0.0.1:8545: too many open files` means you opened so many TCP connections that your OS refused to allow more to be opened. Please reuse existing connections for multiple API calls and not hammer the node with new connections. Alternatively I'd suggest to use the websocket API or IPC if possible.",
